Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:34.39,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}凝视着各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:39.66,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}如今 我仍在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:45.47,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}直至两份心意再次交融
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:49.59,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}纵使迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:54.45,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}仍追忆梦想之色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:57.62,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}正因思念你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:22:00.19,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}我才能坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:01.44,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}我一定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:04.92,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}不会就此停步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:10.07,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}现在 我们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:15.13,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}凝望着那光彩夺目的明日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:20.82,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}你听 你教我的那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:28.22,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}此刻 正在这片天空中回荡
